%% INV-01: junior/senior coverage floor and self-balancing
flowchart TD
    J[juniorTVL] --> R[ratioBps = junior × 10000 / senior]
    S[seniorTVL] --> R
    R --> C{ratio >= minCoverageRatioBps?}
    C -->|Yes| OK[Senior intake allowed]
    C -->|No| BLOCK[Revert CoverageRatioBelowFloor]
    R --> ST[stressLevel → dynamic fee bump]
    ST --> FEE[beforeSwap higher feeBps]
    FEE --> JR[juniorReserve grows from swap split]
    JR --> R

    subgraph withdrawal["Junior exit check"]
        NJ[newJuniorTVL after exit] --> PR[prospective ratio]
        PR --> C2{ratio >= floor?}
        C2 -->|No| BLOCK2[Block junior withdrawal]
    end
